Malaria, Haiti -- Background
----------------------------
A free e-book which summarizes all of the infectious diseases of
Haiti can be accessed at the link above to Gideon.

A link to the book is also available on the ISID home page:
<http://www.isid.org/index.shtml>.

--
Communicated by:
Steve Berger
Geographic Medicine
Tel Aviv Medical Center
<mberger@post.tau.ac.il>

[The e-book provides descriptions of many microorganisms causing
infections in Haiti including malaria and clinical conditions, and
can be downloaded free of charge from the links cited above or directly from:
<http://www.gideononline.com/blog/wp/wp-content/uploads/The-Infectious-Diseases-of-Haiti-by-GIDEON.pdf>.

Our thanks to Prof. Berger and GIDEON for providing this information
to our subscribers. - Mods.EP/MPP]
